snippet.title: Nekotako (2020 SNES Homebrew) Demo - Worlds 1 and 2
snippet.description:
Checking out this adorable new SNES game with music that's somewhere between Kirby and Earthbound (also known as Taco: Princess From the Moon). Get the demo here: https://gyuque.booth.pm/items/2009554 (you have to create an account but it's free, don't be lazy)

00:00 Intro
01:54 Field 1-1
02:35 Field 1-2
03:21 Field 1-3
04:15 Field 1-4
07:10 Field 2-1
08:59 Field 2-2
10:18 Field 2-3
11:40 Field 2-4

Played on MiSTer FPGA, SNES core!

Solo channels
MrMxy: https://www.youtube.com/user/MrMxy
